org.pimslims.business.crystallization.view
Class PlateExperimentView

java.lang.Object
  org.pimslims.business.crystallization.view.PlateExperimentView

public class PlateExperimentView
    
extends java.lang.Object



This is a view class representing a plate and is used in the ViewPlates
Screen of the GUI. It provides a simplified or extended view of a plate
following the requirements of the page rather than an exact definition of the
object (where the model object should be used). This is somewhat similar to a
JSF Backing bean This object represents a "plate", or rather one experiment on a
plate.
